### 2️⃣ Sysmon config to support this detection

You want Sysmon to log detailed process creation, including PowerShell command lines.

**File path in GitHub (suggested):**

`03-Configs/sysmon-config.xml`

In your Sysmon config, ensure you have at least:

```xml
<Sysmon schemaversion="4.50">
  <EventFiltering>
    <ProcessCreate onmatch="include">
      <Image condition="end with">powershell.exe</Image>
    </ProcessCreate>
  </EventFiltering>
</Sysmon>
